<para>Multiple calls accumulate — each call adds an additional handler. Long press fires once when the gesture is detected (on press-down after the time threshold). Press release is reported separately via PressedChangedSignal.</para>
<para>The handler must return bool: return <computeroutput>true</computeroutput> to suppress the subsequent click event, or <computeroutput>false</computeroutput> to allow it.</para>
<para>If <computeroutput>obj</computeroutput> implements ConnectionTrackerInterface, the connection is auto-removed on <computeroutput>obj</computeroutput> destruction.</para>
