    <briefdescription>
<para><ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1InteractiveTrait" kindref="compound">InteractiveTrait</ref> is an interaction trait that provides clickable behavior to a <ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1View" kindref="compound">View</ref>. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1InteractiveTrait" kindref="compound">InteractiveTrait</ref> provides click, long-press, and pressed-state handling functionality. It can be attached to any <ref refid="classDali_1_1Ui_1_1View" kindref="compound">View</ref> to make it interactive. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
